00:59:05,772 --> 00:59:06,870
Another hour.

1101
00:59:07,295 --> 00:59:10,813
No Subir, you are right...

1102
00:59:11,730 --> 00:59:15,055
What can we do?
How long for the train?

1103
00:59:15,368 --> 00:59:17,089
Still 45 minutes.

1104
00:59:17,719 --> 00:59:19,345
45 minutes?

1105
00:59:21,418 --> 00:59:23,831
Hey Debashish,
please bring the script once.

1106
00:59:25,120 --> 00:59:27,633
Hey.
- Shut up.

1107
00:59:27,713 --> 00:59:28,935
Quick, quick!

1108
00:59:29,480 --> 00:59:32,561
Please hold.
