1126
01:00:14,592 --> 01:00:16,672
Come. Order.

1127
01:00:17,982 --> 01:00:18,889
Yeah...

1128
01:00:19,325 --> 01:00:21,277
Roll sound.
- Rolling.

1129
01:00:22,560 --> 01:00:24,838
Roll camera.
