01:09:15,459 --> 01:09:16,580
Then,

1308
01:09:17,543 --> 01:09:19,433
the movie will end on a happy note,

1309
01:09:19,759 --> 01:09:21,081
there will be hope.

1310
01:09:21,749 --> 01:09:24,559
Audience will leave
the hall on a happy note.

