1373
01:12:31,676 --> 01:12:33,257
Who?

1374
01:12:36,635 --> 01:12:37,946
Apu?

1375
01:12:38,995 --> 01:12:40,579
Apu, it's me, Vinku.

1376
01:12:40,659 --> 01:12:42,742
Who? Vinku?

1377
01:12:43,970 --> 01:12:45,081
Come.

1378
01:12:45,626 --> 01:12:50,288
Where? Where are you going, Vinku?

1379
01:12:50,368 --> 01:12:52,830
Vinku!

1380
01:12:54,499 --> 01:12:56,094
See there.

1381
01:13:00,548 --> 01:13:03,515
Is this the owl you were talking...

1382
01:13:04,175 --> 01:13:05,622
Vinku?

1383
01:13:24,751 --> 01:13:26,142
Fire.

1384
01:13:27,156 --> 01:13:28,755
Hey, Apu?
- Apu.

1385
01:13:29,158 --> 01:13:30,578
What are you mumbling?

1386
01:13:31,176 --> 01:13:32,280
Huh?

1387
01:13:32,798 --> 01:13:34,068
What happened?

1388
01:13:34,852 --> 01:13:36,141
No, nothing.

1389
01:13:37,165 --> 01:13:38,646
Just a nightmare.

1390
01:13:39,539 --> 01:13:40,959
No more.

1391
01:13:41,949 --> 01:13:44,374
It seems your advance
cheque is here.

1392
01:13:44,905 --> 01:13:46,084
What? Let me see.

1393
01:13:55,089 --> 01:13:56,315
Correct.

1394
01:13:56,891 --> 01:13:58,938
Let me give my clients
this good news.

1395
01:13:59,319 --> 01:14:00,661
Hey.
- What?

1396
01:14:00,741 --> 01:14:02,009
There's another news.

1397
01:14:02,537 --> 01:14:03,543
What?

1398
01:14:04,004 --> 01:14:06,795
A new family member
is coming to our house.

1399
01:14:07,361 --> 01:14:09,858
