he got your work done.

1400
01:14:11,850 --> 01:14:12,983
What?

1401
01:14:15,612 --> 01:14:17,577
Finally, the lady luck

1402
01:14:17,942 --> 01:14:19,698
was happy on me.

1403
01:14:20,597 --> 01:14:21,626
How?

1404
01:14:21,706 --> 01:14:26,758
I realize that if I only
shoot on Sundays and holidays,

1405
01:14:27,209 --> 01:14:29,907
