1408
01:14:38,287 --> 01:14:40,724
I had a new boss by then,
Mr.Newman.

1409
01:14:41,503 --> 01:14:44,783
Whether he'll be generous
towards me, like Mr. Brown,

1410
01:14:45,262 --> 01:14:46,451
I had no idea.

1411
01:14:46,531 --> 01:14:48,479
I don't know how to thank you,
Mr. Newman.

1412
01:14:48,559 --> 01:14:50,803
I shall always be
obliged to you for this.

1413
01:14:51,277 --> 01:14:52,689
You're welcome, Mr. Ray.

1414
01:14:52,979 --> 01:14:54,954
And I wish you all
the best in your venture.

1415
01:14:55,551 --> 01:14:57,442
You've got a great story to tell.

1416
01:14:57,942 --> 01:15:00,919
And I hope you remember to come back
to us when your shooting is done.

1417
01:15:00,999 --> 01:15:02,147
Certainly, sir.

1418
01:15:02,227 --> 01:15:03,601
