- Nothing kind as such.

1428
01:15:26,699 --> 01:15:29,051
They don't want to
lose an asset like you.

1429
01:15:29,131 --> 01:15:33,187
By the way, I don't want
to lose my cover designer.

1430
01:15:33,267 --> 01:15:36,199
Keep that in mind, later
you'll be the film director and..

1431
01:15:36,279 --> 01:15:38,235
A lot could have
happened in this year.

1432
01:15:38,469 --> 01:15:41,114
With Manik's age,
his voice could have broken.

1433
