01:16:07,609 --> 01:16:09,034
Yes, blanket.

1447
01:16:09,840 --> 01:16:10,827
Hey!

1448
01:16:11,921 --> 01:16:13,179
First position, please.

1449
01:16:13,533 --> 01:16:15,358
Brother, is it fine?
- Yes, fine.

1450
01:16:17,607 --> 01:16:19,063
Yeah, yeah, fine.

1451
01:16:19,143 --> 01:16:20,687
That's enough.
- This is first one.

